    "name": "YanYueDao Kill",
    "steam_appid": 3110000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>声明：本游戏除部分翻译外，没有使用任何生成式AI的素材，代码、剧本、美术、特效、音乐等全流程无AI参与。</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个简单爽快的指令战斗迷宫RPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1、 探索迷宫，丰富有趣的地图要素，开宝箱，打BOSS，收集特殊道具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras/04eabd2904a6908b1c63c355f5bb65d9.avif?t=1770430020\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras_big/04eabd2904a6908b1c63c355f5bb65d9.avif?t=1770430020 width=1560 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2、超爽快指令战斗。战斗只需攻防2键，通过正确打出指令完美抵御敌人的同时，利用即时攻击积累combo放出强力的必杀一击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras/333d136e43526b4fea0ee7a6170eb00c.avif?t=1770430020\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras_big/333d136e43526b4fea0ee7a6170eb00c.avif?t=1770430020 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras/05d7f727aa21cf3decd99530568ad180.avif?t=1770430020\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras_big/05d7f727aa21cf3decd99530568ad180.avif?t=1770430020 width=1560 height=842 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3、培养角色，搭载属性升级系统。即使遭遇强敌，也可提升自身数值后再去挑战完成反杀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4、形形色色的路人们，在迷宫中认识各路人士，听他们讲述奇特经历，从而破解塔中的谜团。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras/ea5f911f4f6f254f70ecc89545aaeeba.avif?t=1770430020\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110000/extras_big/ea5f911f4f6f254f70ecc89545aaeeba.avif?t=1770430020 width=1560 height=838 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
